    "9651803": {
      "title": "Clinical pharmacokinetics of the prodrug oseltamivir and its active metabolite Ro 64-0802",
      "abstract": "Oseltamivir is an ethyl ester prodrug of Ro 64-0802, a selective inhibitor of influenza virus neuraminidase. Oral administration of oseltamivir delivers the active antiviral Ro 64-0802 to the bloodstream, and thus all sites of influenza infection (lung, nasal mucosa, middle ear) are accessible."
